scene.message:
Elly: Kandori... So he too{nl}
has come to{nl}
this city after all.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Even Kandori's{nl}
here now?{nl}
I've got a bad feeling!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Kandori, huh...{waitkey}{clearbox}Even for a guy like me,{nl}
that man's the one{nl}
I'd really rather avoid.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Kandori...{nl}
So he's come to{nl}
this world...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Saves me the search.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: They said there's a{nl}
demon in the subway.{nl}
So, what was it{wait_fr:32}... Ha...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Hamano?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The Mirror of Harming.{nl}
With it, they said,{nl}
one can cross to the east.{waitkey}{clearbox}Taking our city alone{nl}
wasn't enough to{nl}
satisfy Kandori, it seems...{waitkey}I'll teach him greed{nl}
is the root of ruin.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Even if you say that,{nl}
I don't know anything{nl}
about a Mirror of Harming...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmm...{wait_fr:32} I feel{nl}
I've heard that name{nl}
somewhere before...{waitkey}{ctl0f:1}, what do you think?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: The wall splitting this{nl}
city in two went up{nl}
only recently.{waitkey}Before, you could cross{nl}
to the other side freely.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I can't recall...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
The Mirror of Harming...{nl}
I've surely heard{nl}
that name somewhere.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: 'Harming,' huh...{nl}
That's a real{nl}
old-fashioned name.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Something's been{nl}
bugging me, you know...{waitkey}{clearbox}They said there's a 'demon'{nl}
down in the subway, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}...Me{wait_fr:38}, I wouldn't mind{nl}
not crossing east at all,{nl}
y'know... just sayin'...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The 'demon' in the{nl}
subway, huh...{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:21}So we really do{nl}
have to fight that thing...{wait_fr:21}{nl}
...boo-hoo-hoo...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Since ancient times,{nl}
that mirror was believed{nl}
to hold 'Harming' power-{waitkey}the power to break evil,{nl}
or so it's believed.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: If the subway demon{nl}
isn't some gross thing,{nl}
Ayase would be relieved...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...{wait_fr:21}We have to{nl}
fight that monster?{nl}
Waaah, no waaay!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Before you lean on{nl}
others, how about{nl}
thinking for yourself?{waitkey}{ret}
